<p>で、アフタヌーンティーセットを頼みました。</p>
<p><a href="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0620_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-588" src="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0620_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0620_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0620_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a>3段なんですけど、けっこうデカイです。一段目はジャムとクロテッドクリームなど。</p>
<p><a href="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0621_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-589" src="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0621_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0621_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0621_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a>2段目はスコーンなど。</p>
<p><a href="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0622_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-590" src="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0622_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0622_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0622_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a>3段目はサンドイッチなど。</p>
<p><a href="http://i2.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0623_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-591" src="http://i2.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0623_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i2.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0623_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i2.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0623_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a>窓の外にリッツカールトン香港の影が街を覆うのが見えます。でかいビルですねー。</p>
<p><a href="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0627_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-592" src="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0627_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0627_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i1.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0627_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>
<p>ハイティーの時間までオードブルはお休みみたいです。 <a href="http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0642_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-605" src="http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0642_2.jpg?resize=474%2C632" alt="リッツカールトン香港" srcset="http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0642_2.jpg?resize=225%2C300 225w, http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0642_2.jpg?w=480 480w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>
