			<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>
				<a href='http://yoyogiuehara.jp/?attachment_id=578'><img width="200" height="300" src="http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0761_2.jpg?fit=200%2C300" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="オートミール" aria-describedby="gallery-2-578" srcset="http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0761_2.jpg?resize=200%2C300 200w, http://i0.wp.com/yoyogiuehara.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_0761_2.jpg?w=427 427w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></a>
